name: NCDHC Medication Administered Profile
title: NCDHC Medication Administered
description: Medication Statement for NCDHC to represent Vitakin K

binding.description: Medication Administration type( e.g.: Vitamin K) as applicable to NCDHC

element.definition: PBS code from http://pbs.gov.au/code/item. Use of PBS as a code to refer to a type of medication, this excludes implication of context based on the PBS code. Where context is to be implied or stated PBS code needs to be associated with recording a prescription (MedicationRequest) or dispense record(MedicationDispense)
